---
title: Crumbed Chicken Fingers & Plum BBQ Sauce with Cheesy Wedges & Slaw
description: If you don’t want to use a fork we don’t blame you, these chicken fingers are so golden and irresistible in a crunchy crumb that
they need to be dunked in a smokey sweet plum BBQ sauce immediately. Wipe everything up with a side of wedges, covered in
melted Cheddar cheese. We recommend trying them with the sauce too!
